Requirements to run this bot:

-A working internet connection

-A Discord bot user to connect this to
--Note: $selflist and is_self? will need some modification to properly recognize
whatever name you give the bot

-Ruby
--Discordrb
--ruby_jisho

-A C compiler

-Some Unix (Linux, BSD or OSX might work too) for:
--fortune (:fortune, :fortuna)
--/dev/urandom (anything with rng)
--zip (:stallman, :source, :src)

-These files in the same directory:
--config.json (probably going to include an example with some defaults)

-These subdirectories*:
--animals

--memes
---safe
---unverified

--no (images for the bot to refuse to $die)

--quotes
---animu
---general
---vidya
*should be created on launch if they don't exist
